{"tid":1303339,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會講到自己個六七暴動唔係暴動咁叻叻豬,幾時去工聯會切磋下??","createTime":"2019-07-10T09:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T11:43:03.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"705cdcbaa6c4754dd659c959a89496f9a4606d69","tid":1303339,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:37:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/onccnews/videos/409040036370665/?notif_id=1562741595125080&not;if_t=live_video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fonccnews%2Fvideos%2F409040036370665%2F%3Fnotif_id%3D1562741595125080%C2%ACif_t%3Dlive_video&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC7idffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=2bb5dc2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/onccnews/videos/409040036370665/?notif_id=1562741595125080&not;if_t=live_video</a><br />\n<br />\n網上突然有人開始攻擊我哋工聯會，<br />\n我好嬲，我真係好嬲。<br />\n<br />\n係呀！六七暴動我地工聯會嘅弟兄有襲擊警察，有掟燃燒彈！有整炸彈！有燒巴士！有炸死人！咁又點？慘得過政府支持我地咩？早幾日林鄭仲響電視高調多謝我地呢啲建制派呀！<br />\n<br />\n我楊光話你地知，想當年我地工聯會炸死小朋友都冇一絲嘅悔意，燒死埋電台主持都未驚過，歉都冇道過，眼都冇眨過。<br />\n<br />\n挑！我地工聯會元老個個都係參與過六七，好話唔好聽，拎罐午餐肉都掟死你地啦！點會怕你地區區幾百萬香港人？唔好唔記得，你地嘅呀爸呀媽屆屆都支持我地！一車車嚟投我地票！<br />\n<br />\n嗱，畀埋圖你地，夠膽就share出去啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/620332871773292/permalink/639639783175934?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F620332871773292%2Fpermalink%2F639639783175934%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC7idffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=e1b8e36f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/620332871773292/permalink/639639783175934?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n廢青！我都話六七唔係暴動！<br />\n我地後輩，工聯會榮譽會長陳婉嫻早年都響am730專欄講過：「當時社會腐敗，殖民地當權者的壓迫充斥著歧視、欺壓，前輩們的出發點是貧苦大眾的利益！」<br />\n<br />\n雖然我地響街放左過千個炸彈，炸死啲平民，<br />\n我地連小朋友都唔放過，<br />\n但係我要重申：<br />\n我地初心係冇做錯！<br />\n<br />\n我地只係為大眾利益！<br />\n唔好叫我地道歉！<br />\n唔準叫我地暴徒！<br />\n你幾時有見過暴徒有大紫荊？<br />\n你幾時有見過暴徒可以做立法會議員？<br />\n你地咁樣即係質疑一向大公無私嘅香港政府包庇罪犯啦？<br />\n<br />\n你班廢青，炸彈又冇、燒車又冇、燃燒彈又冇，<br />\n憑咩同我地鬥委會、工聯會睇齊？<br />\n唔該你班人認清歷史！"},{"pid":"c408696868b79b972d48208c0ffc5842a37690ed","tid":1303339,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:41:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gwbtRZBkzQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgwbtRZBkzQ4&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC7idffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=a9fe212c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gwbtRZBkzQ4</a>"},{"pid":"2ff2cdec99c1dd923e50da1316d947068ac81f0b","tid":1303339,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94301c47da4540b924935bbf52e552f3cafa2150","tid":1303339,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}